@node "required_sys" "System Requirements"
RCON requires OS 2.04 or higher to run.

There are no special requirements regarding to the type of processor in use.

RCON does not work with some type of shell emulator programs, e.g. Csh.
However, RCON does work if Csh is run in auxiliary mode (Csh -a).

You have to try other shells yourself.
@endnode

